description: Kittens are birthed in their own designated rooms, these private nursery’s allow us to keep a close eye on both Queen and Kittens! Maine Coons are our focus, we do not breed any other type of animal! We have built a huge 18 foot by 34 foot by 6 feet high outdoor cattery for our Maine Coons to enjoy in good weather.  This outside cattery has separate sleeping areas, jungle gym, toys, tunnels, climbing trees, bean bag chairs, wall perches, hammocks, and more.  It is enclosed in strong steel fencing to keep the Maine Coons safe. We are very proud of our new up and coming cattery and feel honored to share this magnificent breed with others!

comments.name: Micheal Lyons
comments.comment: They BLEW the ROOF off at their last event, once everyone started figuring out they were going. This is still simply the greatest opening of an event I have EVER witnessed.

comments.name: Gary Wong
comments.comment: Every time I see him shred I feel so motivated to get off my couch and hop on my board. He’s so talented! I wish I can ride like him one day so I can really enjoy myself!

comments.name: Theodore Duncan
comments.comment: How can someone be so good!!! You can tell he lives for this and loves to do it every day. Every time I see him I feel instantly happy! He’s definitely my favorite ever!
